Python bindings to the [nzb-rs](https://crates.io/crates/nzb-rs) library - a [spec](https://sabnzbd.org/wiki/extra/nzb-spec) compliant parser for [NZB](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NZB) files, written in Rust.

